      "content": "that makes sense for the debate. so if i'm arguing that side, how would i frame the idea of \"cultural preservation\" through segregation? like, instead of just talking about property values, what were the arguments made that segregation actually helped different racial groups maintain their own unique traditions or social structures without interference?",
